ons between the reconstruction and the\nexact solution mainly reflect departures from the log-normal behaviour that are\nascribed to highly non-linear objects in overdense regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jan 2008 18:16:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-01-29"}
